Lol thats the problem with all free bots. Rsbot was amazing for free, although it did get my 128 banned although i got about 90 of those cb levels legit haha. But ya it looks like ima invest in autofighter

Just block it from your isp.

When you host a server, Be smart at it and sue the DDoS fags…
